## Nails to mend your business
Your Ellis Farm is worn and needs mending, but you carry only 0 of the 5 nails a repair takes. Buy the rest, then return to mend it. Ezekiel Crane is here with you and sells nails. Buy it now — call pay_with_item with seller "Ezekiel Crane", item "nail", a qty up to 5, and a payment: coins (amount), goods you carry (pay_items), or both, with consume_now false. Then also use speak for a brief handoff line as you make the offer. They will accept or counter your offer.
Weigh what's in front of you — obligations and pressing needs come before idle matters. Choose one action. After you speak, call done() and let others respond; speak again only if something new happens or someone asks you for more — never repeat or rephrase what you've already said.
